      <section class="section1 statement">
        <div class="text">
          <h2>THE CHALLENGE</h2>
          <p>Managing radioactive waste in the USA is a $500 billion problem. The worst of that waste lasts from ten
            thousand to a billion years.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg"><div class="bg-img"></div></div>
